											"content": [
												{
													"nodeType": "text",
													"data": {
														"target": null,
														"uri": null
													},
													"value": "As cyber attacks continue to evolve and become more sophisticated, it's crucial for organizations to take a proactive approach to security rather than relying solely on reactive measures. Implementing a Zero Trust framework can help prevent potential security breaches, and while it may require some effort to implement, the benefits of a more secure system are well worth it.",
